        <num>10-2-12</num>
        <content>
          <p>In addition to the declarations required by Code Section 10-2-11, any package which is one of a lot containing random weights of the same commodity and bearing the total selling price of the package shall contain a plain and conspicuous declaration of the price per single unit of weight on the outside of the package.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1972, p. 654, ยง 1.)</p>
